.TH SLCONNECTIPV4SOCKET 3 "2026-05-19" "silverlib v1.5.0" "silverlib manual"
.SH NAME
SLConnectIPv4Socket - Connects a socket to a specific destinatary
.SH LIBRARY
silverlib library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #define SILVER_LIB_IMPLEMENTATION
.B #include "silverlib.h"

.BI "int SLConnectIPv4Socket(ConnectionContext" " *ctx" ")"
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Wrapper of \fBconnect\fP(3) function, with logging
and errno printing
.SH RETURN  VALUE
Same return value as \fBconnect\fP(3)
